nodes.text: Nick Kellington (born June 11, 1976) is a British actor and musician who portrayed Bistan in the 2016 Anthology film Rogue One: A Star Wars Story and Snook Uccorfay in Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi.

Kellington also portrays Klaud, Amuncie Tidian, Dellso Prin, and an unnamed character on the planet Pasaana in Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker. In addition, to these performances, he was part of the puppeteering team for the Vexis and puppeteered a worm that watched the puppet show with the Aki-Aki children at the Festival of the Ancestors.

In addition to his work on Star Wars, Kellington is best known for his roles in the  British children's television series In the Night Garden..., ZingZillas and the reboot of Teletubbies; as well as the Netflix series The Dark Crystal: Age of Resistance.
